item.title: Help please?
item.dc:creator: @andrewdawg andrewdawg
item.description:
@andrewdawg wrote:

right click compile, click edit and delete all and add this:

@echo off
title Turbanscape Compiler
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_07\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_07\bin/java.exe” server
pause
